## Why This Changed

This license change was made after the original work (232 commits, 14 plugins, 38 skills) was delivered to a VC-backed company under a $199/month sponsorship arrangement. The company launched their Enterprise 2.0 product featuring "MCP" functionality built from this work, then went silent on compensation discussions.

Future work will require commercial licensing for business use.

For the full story: See `009-temp-data/NIXTLA-EVIDENCE-COMPLETE.md`
